  "title": "IT Infrastructure Support Engineer / Deskstop Support / 5 days  ( Woodalnds ) X2",
  "description": "<p><strong>1. IT Infrastructure Support</strong></p>\n<p>· Maintain and troubleshoot <strong>hardware</strong> (PCs, printers, barcode scanners, etc.)</p>\n<p>· Support <strong>network infrastructure</strong>: LAN/WAN, switches, routers, Wi-Fi</p>\n<p>· Ensure <strong>servers</strong> and <strong>data storage</strong> are running smoothly (file servers, domain controllers)</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><u><strong>Requirement</strong></u></p>\n<p>· <strong>Diploma or Degree</strong> in Information Technology, Computer Science, Engineering, or related field</p>\n<p>· <strong>1–3 years</strong> of experience in IT support, networking, or systems administration</p>\n<p>Good Pay + Good allowance + Good Bonus</p>\n<p>Interested candidates please send an updated Resume / CV in Ms Word format to lilian@recruitflash.com or WhatsApp’s your resume to 98332779 ( no Calls)</p>\n<p>Consultant in-charge : Quah Li Lian (Lilian) ( Registration No: R1983286 )</p>",
